={
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "response_format": { "type": "json_object" },
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a video production assistant. Given a voiceover script, split it into {{ $('2. Set Input Parameters').item.json.num_scenes }} scenes. For each scene, generate a cinematic DALL-E 3 image prompt. Return JSON: { \"scenes\": [{ \"scene_number\": 1, \"voiceover_segment\": \"text for this scene\", \"image_prompt\": \"cinematic wide shot of...\", \"duration_seconds\": 8 }] }. Make image prompts vivid, photorealistic, 16:9 aspect ratio, no text in images. Total duration should roughly match the script length."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": {{ JSON.stringify($('2. Set Input Parameters').item.json.script) }}
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 4000
}

